## Your First 10 Minutes

1. Open [[Glossary]] ‚Äî scan the term tables to orient yourself on domain language
2. Pick any project in `Projects/` ‚Äî follow links to people and concepts
3. Open Graph View (`Cmd+G`) ‚Äî see the full knowledge map
4. Create a Daily Note (`Cmd+T` ‚Üí Daily Note) ‚Äî start capturing your own notes
5. Read `AGENT.md` to see how AI agents navigate this vault

